<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>YOUR SELLER APPLICATION HAS BEEN APPROVED</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f2f6f8;
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
      }

      .wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 30px 12px;
        background-color: #f2f6f8;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 520px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      }

      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
        padding: 28px 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      .header .icon {
        font-size: 40px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.3px;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 28px 24px;
        color: #333333;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .content h2 {
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #1f2937;
      }

      .content p {
        margin: 10px 0;
        font-size: 15px;
      }

      .highlight-box {
        background: #eff6ff;
        border: 1px solid #93c5fd;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 16px 20px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }

      .highlight-box p {
        margin: 6px 0;
        color: #1e40af;
        font-size: 15px;
      }

      .highlight-box p strong {
        color: #1d4ed8;
      }

      .stage-box {
        background: #fef9c3;
        border: 1px solid #fde047;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 14px 18px;
        margin: 16px 0;
      }

      .stage-box p {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #713f12;
      }

      .stage-box .stage-title {
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #92400e;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }

      .limit-list {
        padding-left: 18px;
        margin: 8px 0 0 0;
        color: #713f12;
      }

      .limit-list li {
        margin-bottom: 4px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .upgrade-box {
        background: #f0fdf4;
        border: 1px solid #86efac;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 14px 18px;
        margin: 16px 0;
      }

      .upgrade-box p {
        margin: 0 0 8px 0;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #15803d;
      }

      .upgrade-list {
        padding-left: 18px;
        margin: 0;
        color: #166534;
      }

      .upgrade-list li {
        margin-bottom: 4px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .btn-wrapper {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 24px 0 12px;
      }

      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 32px;
        background: #2563eb;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .footer {
        padding: 16px 24px;
        background: #f8fafc;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #6b7280;
        border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      }

      .footer p {
        margin: 4px 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
          <div class="icon">🎉</div>
          <h1>CONGRATULATIONS! YOU HAVE BECOME A SELLER</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
          <h2>Hello <strong><%= username %></strong>,</h2>
          <p>
            Your account has been automatically upgraded to Seller. You can
            start selling products right away!
          </p>

          <div class="highlight-box">
            <p>🏪 Shop name: <strong><%= shopName %></strong></p>
            <p>📅 Registration date: <strong><%= registeredAt %></strong></p>
            <p>⚡ Status: <strong>PROBATION (Trial)</strong></p>
          </div>

          <div class="stage-box">
            <p class="stage-title">⚠️ PROBATION STAGE – Current Limitations:</p>
            <ul class="limit-list">
              <li>Maximum <strong>5 products/day</strong></li>
              <li>Maximum <strong>10 orders/day</strong></li>
              <li>
                Cannot post products in <strong>high-risk categories</strong>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="upgrade-box">
            <p>🚀 Conditions to upgrade to NORMAL (remove limits):</p>
            <ul class="upgrade-list">
              <li>Have <strong>≥ 20 orders</strong></li>
              <li>Average rating <strong>≥ 4.5 ⭐</strong></li>
              <li>Return rate <strong>&lt; 5%</strong></li>
              <li>Account exists for <strong>&gt; 30 days</strong></li>
              <li>No serious reports</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <p>
            System will automatically check and upgrade your account when you
            meet the conditions. 💪
          </p>

          <div class="btn-wrapper">
            <a
              href="<%= process.env.CLIENT_URL || 'http://localhost:5173' %>/seller"
              class="btn"
            >
              Navigate to Seller Panel
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
          <p>
            &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Ebay Clone. All rights
            reserved.
          </p>
          <p>This email was sent automatically, please do not reply.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
